'''Rafik Belghali''' (born 7 June 2002) is a professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a right-back for Italian {{Italian football updater|HellasVerona}} club [[Hellas Verona FC|Hellas Verona]]. Born in Belgium, he represents the [[Algeria national football team|Algeria national team]].

==Club career==
On 28 June 2023, Belghali signed a three-season contract with [[K.V. Mechelen|Mechelen]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Mechelen|url=https://www.kvmechelen.be/2023-2024/rafik-belghali-zomertransfer-2|title=Rafik Belghali is tweede zomertransfer|trans-title=Rafik Belghali is second summer transfer|date=28 June 2023|access-date=7 September 2023|language=nl}}</ref>

On 19 August 2025, Belghali moved to [[Hellas Verona FC|Hellas Verona]] in Italy with a four-season contract.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Hellas Verona FC|url=https://www.hellasverona.it/news/benvenuto-rafik-belghali-e-un-nuovo-difensore-gialloblu|title=Benvenuto Rafik! Belghali è un nuovo difensore gialloblù|trans-title=Welcome Rafik! Belghali is a new Gialloblu defender.|date=19 August 2025|access-date=19 August 2025|language=it}}</ref>

==International career==
In March 2022, Belghali was called up by [[Noureddine Ould Ali]] to the [[Algeria national under-23 football team|Algeria under-23 national team]] for the first time for a pair of friendlies against Mauritania.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.faf.dz/equipe-nationale-u23-ould-ali-convoque-23-joueurs-pour-la-mauritanie/|title=EQUIPE NATIONALE U23 : OULD ALI CONVOQUE 23 JOUEURS POUR LA MAURITANIE|author=FAF.dz|date=March 19, 2022|accessdate=March 23, 2022|language=French}}</ref>

In his maiden call up to the [[Algeria national football team|Algerian national team]], Belghali started in a friendly against Zimbabwe on November 13, 2025.<ref>https://www.vavel.com/en-us/soccer/2025/11/13/1241112-algeria-vs-zimbabwe-live-score-friendly.html</ref>

==Personal life==
Belghali was born in Belgium to Algerian parents.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dzfoot.com/2021/03/13/belgique-ishak-boussouf-dans-le-groupe-de-lommel-199760.php|title=Belgique : Ishak Boussouf dans le groupe de Lommel|author=Walid Ziani|publisher=DZfoot|language=French|date=March 13, 2021|accessdate=March 22, 2021}}</ref>

